  linesWarn:
  - Don't even think about it.
  - Hands. Now.
  - I've seen your type before.
  linesDemandBribe:
  - Maybe we can work something out. Maybe.
  - You've got ten seconds to make it worth my while.
  linesAcceptBribe:
  - This conversation never happened.
  - Get out of my sight.
  linesRejectBribe:
  - Wrong answer.
  - You had your chance.
  - I was hoping you'd say that.
  linesArrest:
  - You're done.
  - Face down. Don't make me ask twice.
  linesAttack:
  - I've been waiting for this.
  - Wrong move.
  - You just made my day.
